WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.537
Cockroach Crawler gives agent workflows a bounded path to public

00:00:03.537 --> 00:00:06.574
web evidence. It is not a browser free-for-all.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:14.354
The hardened Node CLI validates every seed, DNS answer, redirect,

00:00:14.354 --> 00:00:18.209
robots rule, and byte budget before network dispatch.

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.419
Source doctor reports what is actually available. Web and public

00:00:23.419 --> 00:00:26.339
GitHub are ready. YouTube is partial. X and Reddit need

00:00:26.339 --> 00:00:29.258
official credentials.

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:34.566
A separate serverless Worker accepts only allowlisted HTTPS origins, requires

00:00:34.566 --> 00:00:38.632
a bearer secret, rate limits requests, and fails closed.

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:43.228
The complete local Node suite passes. A separate one hundred

00:00:43.228 --> 00:00:45.956
twenty page fixture checks regressions. It is not an industry

00:00:45.956 --> 00:00:48.685
or global benchmark.

00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:53.079
Use stable zero point two today, or review the zero

00:00:53.079 --> 00:00:55.659
point three alpha candidate in source. Understand the boundary before

00:00:55.659 --> 00:00:58.238
you trust the output.
